      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained, making it a perfect choice for anyone looking for a dependable ride. It shows some light, honest wear from regular use, but it runs smoothly and is ready to hit the road today. You'll love the balance of quality and value this car offers!",
