    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior still maintains a strong gloss, though you will notice some minor road rash and a few light surface scratches upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of any major odors or tears, showing only light wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it remains very reliable, offering a smooth ride and consistent performance that makes it a great choice for anyone looking for a dependable, high-quality pre-owned vehicle.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a practical choice for a buyer who prioritizes reliable transportation over a flawless appearance. Mechanically, the car is solid; the engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a dependable daily driver. However, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows typical wear and tear from regular use. It has been recently serviced and is ready for the road, offering a great balance of functionality and affordability for someone who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, reflects a standard of care synonymous with investment-grade quality. Mechanically superior and aesthetically without peer, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the collector who demands excellence without compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
